.DT
set_max_gp
Discworld living help
set_max_gp

Name
.SI 5
set_max_gp - Sets the maximun gps.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_max_gp(int mgp);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This sets the maximun gps for the object.  The current guild points
are scalled.  This means if you set the max gps to say 100 from 50
the current gps were 25, when this function had finished the current
gps would be 25.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_max_gp, adjust_max_gp, query_gp
.EP
